Other metrics suggestions for the Sub-Scores

In order to evaluate the effects of each sub-score in the form of metrics representing the participants’ gaming strategies, we suggest: - For the Fortress Score : the total of destroyed fortress - For the Flight Score : the total of “bad” flight events (border collision, fortress collision, ship damage) - For the Bonus Score : the percentage of captured bonuses during the game - For the Mine Score : the percentage of destroyed mines during the game
